short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Cloud-based Google Map Editor. Create your own map or business locator online and embed in web page easily for mobile compatibility.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Create, save, edit interactive maps in browser.

Easily embed maps to websites by just copy and paste.
Access your maps everywhere, on all your devices.

- Pinpoint locations using address, ZIP code, longitude & latitude to show your branches, offices, properties and amenities accurately
- Add color, annotations, mouse rollover effects to maps and embedding in web pages, reports and presentations
- Easily show market analysis and predictions at your next 
meeting with business data on country or regional maps
- Create itineraries with easy-to-read route maps to 
show and plan trips
